.Dd November 7, 2014
.Dt SHTK_VERSION_IS 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm shtk_version_is
.Nd Checks if shtk is a specific version
.Sh LIBRARY
shtk_import version
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Ar version
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
function checks if the version of the in-use
.Nm shtk
is exactly
.Ar version .
.Sh RETURN VALUES
.Nm
returns 0 (true) if the in-use
.Nm shtk
is version
.Ar version ;
1 (false) otherwise.
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Bd -literal -offset indent
if shtk_version_is 1.8; then
    # Test for a known bug, for example, and work it around.
fi
.Ed
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr shtk 3 ,
.Xr shtk_version 3
.Sh HISTORY
.Nm
first appeared in
.Nm shtk
1.5.
